<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Unified Algebra Stack Dashboard</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --bg: #0f172a;
            --panel: #111827;
            --panel-light: #1e293b;
            --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            --text: #e5e7eb;
            --muted: #94a3b8;
            --green: #22c55e;
            --amber: #f59e0b;
            --blue: #3b82f6;
            --purple: #8b5cf6;
            --red: #ef4444;
            --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #020617 0%, #0f172a 100%);
            color: var(--text);
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .dashboard {
            max-width: 1600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .hero {
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.75);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 28px;
            padding: 32px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
        }

        .hero-top {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .hero p {
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .status-pill {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.12);
            color: #86efac;
            border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2);
            padding: 12px 18px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .pulse {
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            background: var(--green);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: pulse 1.5s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% {
                transform: scale(1);
                opacity: 1;
            }

            50% {
                transform: scale(1.5);
                opacity: 0.4;
            }

            100% {
                transform: scale(1);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        .hero-metrics {
            margin-top: 28px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 18px;
        }

        .metric-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 22px;
            padding: 22px;
        }

        .metric-card span {
            display: block;
            color: var(--muted);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .metric-card h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .metric-card small {
            color: #86efac;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        .grid-3 {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .panel {
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.75);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 24px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }

        .panel-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .panel h3 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .subtle {
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .timeline {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 18px;
        }

        .timeline-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .timeline-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 4px;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--blue), var(--purple));
        }

        .timeline-time {
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .timeline-card h4 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
        }

        .diff {
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 14px;
            margin-top: 12px;
            color: #cbd5e1;
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .verify {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 14px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .tag {
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        }

        .green {
            background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.12);
            color: #86efac;
        }

        .blue {
            background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.12);
            color: #93c5fd;
        }

        .amber {
            background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.12);
            color: #fcd34d;
        }

        .intent-flow {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 24px;
            gap: 12px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .intent-step {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 120px;
            text-align: center;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 18px;
        }

        .arrow {
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .node-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
            gap: 18px;
        }

        .node {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border-radius: 18px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 18px;
        }

        .node-status {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 12px;
            color: #86efac;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .assistant {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.18), rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15));
            border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.25);
        }

        .assistant-box {
            margin-top: 20px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
            border-radius: 18px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            padding: 18px;
            color: #dbeafe;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .assistant-input {
            margin-top: 18px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .assistant-input input {
            flex: 1;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            color: white;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            outline: none;
        }

        .assistant-input button {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--purple));
            border: none;
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 14px 22px;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .footer-note {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            body {
                padding: 16px;
            }

            .hero {
                padding: 24px;
            }

            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 1.7rem;
            }

            .intent-flow {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .arrow {
                transform: rotate(90deg);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="dashboard">

        <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-top">
                <div>
                    <h1>Unified Algebra Stack</h1>
                    <p>
                        Human-centric deterministic runtime dashboard with replay visibility,
                        cryptographic integrity, causal state transitions, and distributed synchronization insight.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="status-pill">
                    <div class="pulse"></div>
                    Runtime Stable
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-metrics">
                <div class="metric-card">
                    <span>Verified Transitions</span>
                    <h2>12,402</h2>
                    <small>Replay consistent</small>
                </div>

                <div class="metric-card">
                    <span>Determinism Score</span>
                    <h2>100%</h2>
                    <small>No divergences detected</small>
                </div>

                <div class="metric-card">
                    <span>Event Throughput</span>
                    <h2>4,820/s</h2>
                    <small>Stable processing load</small>
                </div>

                <div class="metric-card">
                    <span>Distributed Nodes</span>
                    <h2>18</h2>
                    <small>All synchronized</small>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="grid-3">

            <div class="panel">
                <div class="panel-header">
                    <h3>Current Runtime State</h3>
                    <span class="subtle">Live snapshot</span>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline">
                    <div class="timeline-card">
                        <h4>Operational Summary</h4>
                        <p class="subtle">
                            Runtime healthy. Intent queue processing normally with stable replay consistency.
                        </p>

                        <div class="diff">
                            activeSessions: 1,204
                            <br>
                            pendingIntents: 12
                            <br>
                            replayLatency: 14ms
                            <br>
                            checkpointDepth: 12,402
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="panel">
                <div class="panel-header">
                    <h3>Intent Pipeline</h3>
                    <span class="subtle">Effect execution</span>
                </div>

                <div class="intent-flow">
                    <div class="intent-step">
                        <strong>REDUCE</strong>
                        <p class="subtle">Event accepted</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="arrow">→</div>

                    <div class="intent-step">
                        <strong>INTENTS</strong>
                        <p class="subtle">Effects generated</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="arrow">→</div>

                    <div class="intent-step">
                        <strong>EXECUTE</strong>
                        <p class="subtle">Distributed actions</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="arrow">→</div>

                    <div class="intent-step">
                        <strong>VERIFY</strong>
                        <p class="subtle">Replay confirmed</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="panel">
                <div class="panel-header">
                    <h3>Replay Integrity</h3>
                    <span class="subtle">Audit confidence</span>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-card">
                    <h4>Deterministic Verification</h4>

                    <div class="diff">
                        replayedCheckpoints: 12,402
                        <br>
                        divergences: 0
                        <br>
                        hashIntegrity: VALID
                        <br>
                        reducerPurity: VERIFIED
                    </div>

                    <div class="verify">
                        <div class="tag green">✓ Replay Stable</div>
                        <div class="tag blue">✓ Hash Linked</div>
                        <div class="tag amber">0 Pending Repairs</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </section>

        <section class="panel">
            <div class="panel-header">
                <h3>State Transition Timeline</h3>
                <span class="subtle">Human-readable runtime history</span>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline">

                <div class="timeline-card">
                    <div class="timeline-time">12:04:22 PM</div>
                    <h4>Deposit workflow completed</h4>

                    <p class="subtle">
                        Runtime processed a deterministic balance update and generated persistence intents.
                    </p>

                    <div class="diff">
                        balance: 1000 → 1200
                        <br>
                        pendingSettlements: 3 → 2
                        <br>
                        intentsGenerated: [LOG, STORE]
                    </div>

                    <div class="verify">
                        <div class="tag green">✓ Replay Verified</div>
                        <div class="tag blue">✓ Hash Valid</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-card">
                    <div class="timeline-time">12:03:41 PM</div>
                    <h4>Node synchronization event</h4>

                    <p class="subtle">
                        Distributed runtime clocks converged after temporary network delay.
                    </p>

                    <div class="diff">
                        hlcDrift: 12ms → 2ms
                        <br>
                        synchronizedNodes: 17 → 18
                    </div>

                    <div class="verify">
                        <div class="tag green">✓ Cluster Healthy</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-card">
                    <div class="timeline-time">12:01:18 PM</div>
                    <h4>Replay audit completed</h4>

                    <p class="subtle">
                        Historical execution replay matched canonical state lineage.
                    </p>

                    <div class="diff">
                        checkpointsReplayed: 12,402
                        <br>
                        replayConsistency: 100%
                    </div>

                    <div class="verify">
                        <div class="tag green">✓ Deterministic</div>
                        <div class="tag blue">✓ Audit Passed</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="grid-3">

            <div class="panel">
                <div class="panel-header">
                    <h3>Distributed Nodes</h3>
                    <span class="subtle">Synchronization topology</span>
                </div>

                <div class="node-grid">
                    <div class="node">
                        <strong>Node-01</strong>
                        <div class="node-status">
                            <div class="pulse"></div>
                            Synchronized
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="node">
                        <strong>Node-02</strong>
                        <div class="node-status">
                            <div class="pulse"></div>
                            Synchronized
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="node">
                        <strong>Node-03</strong>
                        <div class="node-status">
                            <div class="pulse"></div>
                            Drift 2ms
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="node">
                        <strong>Node-04</strong>
                        <div class="node-status">
                            <div class="pulse"></div>
                            Healthy
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="panel">
                <div class="panel-header">
                    <h3>Hash Chain Integrity</h3>
                    <span class="subtle">Checkpoint lineage</span>
                </div>

                <div class="diff">
                    checkpoint-12400
                    <br>
                    ↓
                    <br>
                    checkpoint-12401
                    <br>
                    ↓
                    <br>
                    checkpoint-12402
                </div>

                <div class="verify" style="margin-top:20px;">
                    <div class="tag green">No tampering detected</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="panel assistant">
                <div class="panel-header">
                    <h3>AI Runtime Assistant</h3>
                    <span class="subtle">Operational explainability</span>
                </div>

                <div class="assistant-box">
                    "Checkpoint 12402 changed because a validated deposit event triggered a deterministic reducer transition. Two intents were emitted: STORE and LOG. Replay verification confirmed identical state reproduction across all synchronized nodes."
                </div>

                <div class="assistant-input">
                    <input type="text" placeholder="Ask why a state transition occurred...">
                    <button>Analyze</button>
                </div>
            </div>

        </section>

        <div class="footer-note">
            Unified Algebra Stack • Human-Centric Deterministic Runtime Interface
        </div>

    </div>

</body>

</html>
